
<div id="stories_new">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-6">
			<h2>Share your story</h2>
			<p class="lead">If you've had an abortion, we encourage you to share your story. There is no "right" story for Project Voice.</p>
			<p class="lead">Before you submit, please read the following:</p>
		
		<ul class="list">
			<li>We welcome firsthand accounts. If you know someone who has had an abortion, please encourage them to submit their own story.</li>
			<li>Focus on your own experiences; refrain from generalizing, assuming, or speaking for others.</li>
			<li>Avoid using names or identifying characteristics of anyone involved in your story.</li>
			<li>Project Voice is not a space for political messages. It is a space for personal stories only.</li>
			<li>And please upload a photo of your hands! We feel that the photos add a sense of personality and diversity to the stories, while maintaining anonymity. The many different hands and creative ways of photographing them add a visual presence to Project Voice.</li>

		</ul>
		<p class="hands">
			<% @examples.each do |example| %>
				<%= circle_hands_thumb(example) %>
			<% end %>
		</p>

		</div>
		<div class="col-md-6">
			<%= form_for(@story) do |f| %>
			    <div class="row">
			    	<div class="col-md-6">
			    		<div class="field">
				    		<%= f.label :country %>
							<%= f.country_select(:country, {priority: %w(US CA), prompt: 'Please select a country'}, {class: 'form-control'}) %>
			    		</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-md-6">
						<div class="field">
							<%= f.label :state %>
							<%= render partial: 'subregion_select', locals: {parent_region: f.object.country} %>
						</div>
			    	</div>
			    </div>
			    <div class="row">
					<div class="col-md-6">
						<div class="field">
				    		<%= f.label :age %>
				    		<%= f.text_field :age, class: 'form-control' %>
						</div>
			    	</div>
			    	<div class="col-md-6">
			    		<div class="field">
						    <span class="btn btn-default btn-file">
						    	<%= f.file_field :photo %>Photo
							</span> 
			    		</div>
					</div>
			    </div>
			    <div class="row">
			    	<div class="col-md-6">
			    		<div class="field">
				    		<%= f.label :email %>
				    		<%= f.text_field :email, class: 'form-control' %>
			    		</div>
			    	</div>
			    	<div class="col-md-6">
			    		<div class="field">
				    		<%= label :email_confirmation, 'Confirm email' %>
				    		<%= f.text_field(:email_confirmation, {class: 'form-control'})%>
			    		</div>
			    	</div>
			    </div>
			    <div class="row">
			    	<div class="col-md-12">
			    		<div class="field">
				    		<%= label :orginal, 'Your story' %>
	   					    <%= f.text_area :original, class: 'form-control' %>
			    		</div>
			    	</div>
			    </div>


			    <% if @story.errors.any? %>
    <div id="" class="alert alert-danger">
      <p><%= pluralize(@story.errors.count, "error") %> prohibited this story from being saved:</p>
      <ul>
      <% @story.errors.full_messages.each do |message| %>
        <li><%= message %></li>
      <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  <% end %>
			    <%= f.submit 'Submit', class: "btn btn-default" %>
			    <hr>
			    <p>Questions?  Contact us: <a href="mailto:info@projectvoice.org">info@projectvoice.org</a></p>
			<% end %>

		</div>

	</div>

</div>
